Interface MLEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SparkListenerEvent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FitEnd, FitStart, LoadInstanceEnd, LoadInstanceStart, SaveInstanceEnd, SaveInstanceStart, TransformEnd, TransformStart

    public interface MLEvent
extends SparkListenerEvent
    Event emitted by ML operations. Events are either fired before and/or after each operation (the event should document this).

    Note:
    This is supported via Pipeline and PipelineModel.
